{"tid":167684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港01:曾俊華陣營估計暫獲400票","createTime":"2017-03-23T04:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T12:33:32.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4700717aa7742aa1c9c317894da36518cc83869c","tid":167684,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"多個民主派政黨和選委本周陸續表態支持曾俊華，其中「民主300+」逾九成選委決定票投薯片，但最大對手林鄭月娥獲建制陣營力撐，包括手握逾百票的民建聯，令曾俊華陷入「贏民望、輸選情」的局面。<br />\n<br />\n踏入選戰最後階段，曾俊華連日不斷致電選委作最後拉票，希望選委願意在暗票階段支持他。有曾營中人估計，曾俊華除獲民主派選委支持外，亦獲分別來自宗教界、商界、紡織及製衣界等界別選委支持，加上有信心力保提名曾俊華的35張建制票，相信曾俊華暫時得票有「4字頭」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/79634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F79634&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=08a0cb5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/79634</a>"},{"pid":"9b2670bb0406df0b9c7baed7fb16649cb7fea60d","tid":167684,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:23:44.000Z","msg":"工聯會聽日表態就玩完啦"},{"pid":"cb5d9cfe99529cd054877ea09c41957f1e051bb4","tid":167684,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"發夢可以勝"},{"pid":"ebb76cca695bd8fda4dbf3fbbbe29f84c10a5201","tid":167684,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工聯會聽日表態就玩完啦</blockquote><br />\n民賤聯都好似係聽日,只要話全投淋病就唔洗玩"},{"pid":"d104cc624bdaafe8c81b0a5c02df6b6db2c2bbe8","tid":167684,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4e53ef02b9fbd091b414fd89bf59c68f3062aa","tid":167684,"uid":84265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"小圈子選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩舊都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets